name: Kaleider Collider
description: Kaleider Collider is a collaborative digital artwork from HeyHazmus and Kadine James. It represents HeyHazmus' interpretation of Kadine's scintillating and multiplicitous influence on the industries and individuals occupying the metaverse. The artwork is a kaleidoscopic mash of a photogrammetry scan of Kadine animated in Blender and baked with themes of 'stepping into the light', colourful passions and ecstatic unbounded creation.
